\c 9
\s IN\nd kosi\nd* izachitha izizwe zeKhanani
\p
\v 1 Zwana, Israyeli; uzachapha iJordani lamuhla, ukungenela ukudla ilifa lezizwe\x + 11.31. 12.10. Josh. 1.11.\x* ezinkulu lezilamandla kulawe, imizi emikhulu\x + 7.1.\x* ebiyelwe ngemithangala efika emazulwini\x + 1.28.\x*.
\v 2 Abantu abakhulu labade, abantwana bamaAnaki wena obaziyo, wena osuzwile \add ngabo kuthiwa\add*: Ngubani ongema phambi kwabantwana bakaAnaki\x + Nani 13.22.\x*?
\v 3 Ngakho yazi lamuhla ukuthi yiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho echapha phambi kwakho\x + 31.3. Josh. 3.11.\x*, engumlilo oqothulayo\x + 4.24.\x*; yona izabachitha, njalo yona izabehlisela phansi phambi kwakho\x + 7.23.\x*; njalo lizabaxotsha basuke elifeni labo, libabhubhise masinyane, njengokutsho kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuwe\x + Eks. 23.31. Dute. 7.24. Eks. 15.9.\x*.
\v 4 Ungakhulumi enhliziyweni yakho, lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho isibaxotshile phambi kwakho, usithi: Ngenxa yokulunga kwami iN\nd kosi\nd* ingingenise ukudla ilifa lelizwe leli\x + 8.17.\x*. Kodwa ngenxa yobubi balezizizwe iN\nd kosi\x + Gen 15.16. Levi 18.24,25. Dute. 18.12.\x*\nd* izixotsha zisuke elifeni lazo phambi kwakho\x + Eks. 23.31. Dute. 7.24. Eks. 15.9.\x*.
\v 5 Kakungenxa yokulunga kwakho kumbe ngenxa yobuqotho benhliziyo yakho ukuthi ungene ukudla ilifa lelizwe lazo\x + Tit. 3.5.\x*; kodwa ngenxa yobubi balezizizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izixotsha zisuke elifeni lazo phambi kwakho\x + Eks. 23.31. Dute. 7.24. Eks. 15.9.\x*, lokuthi iqinise ilizwi iN\nd kosi\nd* eyalifungela oyihlo, uAbrahama, uIsaka loJakobe\x + Gen. 50.24.\x*.
\v 6 Yazi-ke ukuthi kakungenxa yokulunga kwakho ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ikunika lelilizwe elihle ukuthi udle ilifa lalo; ngoba uyisizwe esilentamo elukhuni\x + 9.13. Eks. 32.9. Dute. 10.16. 2 Kho. 17.14. Zaga 29.1.\x*.
\s Abantwana bakoIsrayeli bavukela iN\nd kosi\nd* enkangala
\p
\v 7 Khumbula, ungakhohlwa, ukuthi wayithukuthelisa iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho enkangala; kusukela osukwini owaphuma ngalo elizweni leGibhithe laze lafika kulindawo, beliyivukela iN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 14.11. 16.2. 17.2. Nani 11.4. 20.2. 25.2. Dute. 31.27.\x*\nd*.
\v 8 LeHorebe layithukuthelisa iN\nd kosi\nd*, yaze yalithukuthelela iN\nd kosi\nd* ukulichitha\x + Eks. 32.4. Hlab. 106.19.\x*.
\v 9 Sengenyukele entabeni ukwemukela izibhebhe zamatshe, izibhebhe zesivumelwano iN\nd kosi\nd* eyasenza lani\x + Eks. 24.12,15.\x*, ngasengihlala entabeni insuku ezingamatshumi amane lobusuku obungamatshumi amane, angidlanga sinkwa, anginathanga manzi\x + Eks. 24.18. 34.28.\x*.
\v 10 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasinginika lezozibhebhe ezimbili zamatshe zilotshwe ngomunwe kaNkulunkulu, laphezu kwazo \add kulotshiwe\add* ngokwamazwi wonke iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayiwakhulume lani entabeni, iphakathi komlilo\x + Eks. 31.18.\x* ngosuku lokuhlangana\x + Eks. 19.17. Dute. 4.10. 10.4. 18.16.\x*.
\v 11 Kwasekusithi ekupheleni kwensuku ezingamatshumi amane lobusuku obungamatshumi amane, iN\nd kosi\nd* yangipha izibhebhe ezimbili zamatshe, izibhebhe zesivumelwano.
\v 12 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kimi: Sukuma wehle ngokuphangisa usuke lapha, ngoba abantu bakho owabakhupha eGibhithe bonakalisile\x + Eks. 32.7,8.\x*, baphambukile ngokuphangisa endleleni engabalaya yona, bazenzela isithombe esibunjwe ngokuncibilikisa\x + 9.16. Dute. 31.29. Hlu. 2.17.\x*.
\v 13 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kimi isithi: Ngibabonile lababantu\x + Eks. 32.9.\x*, khangela-ke, bangabantu abantamo zilukhuni\x + 9.6.\x*.
\v 14 Ngiyekela ukuze ngibabhubhise\x + Hlu. 11.37. Eks. 32.10.\x*, ngesule ibizo labo lisuke ngaphansi kwamazulu\x + 29.20. 7.24.\x*; njalo ngizakwenza ube yisizwe esilamandla lesikhulu kulabo\x + Nani 14.12.\x*.
\v 15 Ngasengiphenduka ngisehla entabeni\x + Eks. 32.15.\x*, lentaba yayivutha umlilo; lezibhebhe zombili zesivumelwano zazisezandleni zami zombili\x + 4.11. 5.23. Eks. 19.18.\x*.
\v 16 Ngasengibona, khangelani-ke, lalonile eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wenu, lalizenzele ithole elibunjwe ngokuncibilikisa, laliphambukile ngokuphangisa endleleni iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayililayile\x + Eks. 32.19.\x*.
\v 17 Ngasengibamba izibhebhe zombili, ngazilahla ezandleni zami zombili, ngazibulala phambi kwamehlo enu.
\v 18 Ngasengiziwisela phansi phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 9.25. Eks. 34.28. Hlab. 106.23.\x*\nd* njengakuqala, insuku ezingamatshumi amane lobusuku obungamatshumi amane\x + 9.9.\x*, ngingadli sinkwa, nginganathi manzi, ngenxa yaso sonke isono senu elisonileyo, lisenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, liyithukuthelisa\x + 4.25.\x*.
\v 19 Ngoba ngangisesaba ukuthukuthela lolaka iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayilithukuthelela ngakho ukulibhubhisa; kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* yangizwa langalesosikhathi\x + Eks. 32.10,14,33,34. 33.17. Dute. 10.10.\x*.
\v 20 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimthukuthelela kakhulu uAroni ukuze imbhubhise; kodwa ngamkhulekela loAroni ngalesosikhathi\x + Eks. 32.20.\x*.
\v 21 Ngasengithatha isono senu, ithole elalilenzile, ngalitshisa ngomlilo, ngalichoboza, ngalicholisisa laze laba lincinyane njengothuli; ngaphosa uthuli lwalo esifuleni esasisehla entabeni.
\v 22 LeTabera\x + Num 11.1,3.\x*, leMasa\x + Eks. 17.7.\x*, leKiribothi-Hathava\x + Nani 11.4,34.\x* laliyithukuthelisa iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 23 Lalapho iN\nd kosi\nd* yalithuma lisuka eKadeshi-Bhaneya\x + Nani 13.3,26; 14.1.\x* isithi: Yenyukani, lidle ilifa lelizwe engilinike lona, laselihlamukela umlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu, kaliyikholwanga, kalilalelanga ilizwi layo\x + Hlab. 106.24,25.\x*.
\v 24 Lalivele liyivukele iN\nd kosi\nd* kusukela osukwini engalazi ngalo\x + 9.7. Dute. 31.27.\x*.
\v 25 Ngasengiziwisela phansi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* insuku ezingamatshumi amane lobusuku obungamatshumi amane, engaziwisela phansi ngazo\x + 9.18.\x*, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yayithe izalichitha.
\v 26 Ngasengikhuleka eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ngathi: Nkosi Jehova, ungabachithi abantu bakho lelifa lakho, obahlenge ngobukhulu bakho, owabakhupha eGibhithe ngesandla esilamandla\x + Eks. 32.11-13.\x*.
\v 27 Khumbula inceku zakho, uAbrahama, uIsaka, loJakobe; ungakhangeli inkani yalababantu lobubi babo lesono sabo,
\v 28 hlezi ilizwe owasikhupha kilo lithi: Ngenxa yokuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* yayingelamandla okubangenisa elizweni eyabathembisa lona, langenxa yokuthi ibazonda, yabakhupha ukuze ibabulalele enkangala\x + Nani 14.16.\x*.
\v 29 Kube kanti bangabantu bakho lelifa lakho, owabakhupha ngamandla akho amakhulu langengalo yakho eyeluliweyo\x + 1 Kho. 8.51. Neh. 1.10. Dute. 4.20.\x*.